Located just west of Davis in Dixon, California, Pleasant Valley Recording Studio (formerly Squirty Records) offers a comfortable atmosphere in which to record and edit acoustic music. Lifetime local Matt Dudman, founder of Squirty Records, has been recording and performing for over two decades, with expertise in recording, editing, packaging, promoting, producing and engineering bluegrass, oldtime country, and all other acoustic music. Matt is also available as a studio session musician. With the use of topnotch equipment and years of experience, Squirty Records can provide you with the quality you desire.

Pleasant Valley Recording Studio has had the opportunity to work with well known clients such as Keith Little, Bottom Dwellers, Rick Harris and many more.

For more info see http://www.PleasantValleyMusic.com/ or call (530) 4003872
